#                                                                                                                                                                                                       

[media]

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

[media]

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

[media]

**Simian Style:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

[media]

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

[media]

**UG Launch Bonus** 
- Players can claim a free UG Egg Doo
- New UG Launch Bundle: UG Face, UG Belt, and Pouchie Hat

**Halloween Update**
- New Bat-tlepass featuring the Pet Bat (Pet Fly skin), Bat Hat, Bat Boomerang, Bat Glasses, and Bat Wings
- The return of Candy Hunt and Horror Mode
- Zombie skin unlocked for all monkeys for October
- Updated spooky skyboxes for Crash Site and other levels
